    CPU
        PowerPC

    SYNOPSIS
        AddHeadPPC(_PowerPCBase, list, node)
                   r3            r4    r5

        void AddHeadPPC(struct Library *, struct List*, struct Node*);

    FUNCTION
        Insert a node to the head of a standard exec list. This is the
        mirror function of exec/AddHead.

    INPUTS
