@Node AddPortPPC

powerpc.library/AddPortPPC                          powerpc.library/AddPortPPC

    NAME
        AddPortPPC - adds a public PPC message port to the system (V11)

    CPU
        PowerPC

    SYNOPSIS
        AddPortPPC(_PowerPCBase, MsgPortPPC)
                   r3            r4

