@Node AddTimePPC

powerpc.library/AddTimePPC                          powerpc.library/AddTimePPC

    NAME
        AddTimePPC - adds one time request to another (V7)

    CPU
        PowerPC

    SYNOPSIS
        AddTimePPC(_PowerPCBase, Dest, Source)
                   r3            r4    r5

        void AddTimePPC(struct Library *, struct timeval *, struct timeval *);

